task.en: Preview the Japanese version of the passage "Matterhorn Man".
task.zh: 打开日语版的《马特洪山区人》的快速查看界面。
task.ar: عاين النسخة اليابانية من المقالة "Matterhorn Man".
task.ja: 「マッターホルン山区人」の日本語版をプレビューしてください。

pre_command: open /Users/ec2-user/Desktop; osascript -e 'tell application "Finder" to close windows' && rm -rf /Users/ec2-user/Documents/benchmark_files/ && cp -r /Users/ec2-user/Benchmark_Backup/benchmark_files /Users/ec2-user/Documents && open /Users/ec2-user/Documents/benchmark_files/NCE/Title
grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "マッターホルンの男" && osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "Quick Look" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "マッターホルンの男" && osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "快速查看" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "マッターホルンの男" && osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "معاينة سريعة" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "マッターホルンの男" && osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXTitle" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "Просмотр" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep -q "マッターホルンの男" && echo "True" || echo "False"
